{"tid":1857303,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【掃罩暴龍】遇肺炎 我即刻搶口罩","createTime":"2020-02-02T06:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T07:41:30.000Z","uid":103783,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"011a88cf9f435c86b054890a3fb050011eb11dd2","tid":1857303,"uid":103783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:28:42.000Z","msg":"《自動加價 Let's Buy》<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">原曲:【數碼暴龍01 OP】自動勝利 Let's Fight (鄭伊健) / Butter-Fly (和田光司)</span><br />\n<br />\n<code>#</code>為個罩四撲便喘氣 龍尾有貨了又再起<br />\n通頂相信 頭廿個 我定必勝利<br />\n<br />\n越斷貨個價越高企 入網店要到廿六世紀<br />\n返貨相信 下禮拜 我定必勝利<br />\n<br />\n來全情 炒 炒 炒 炒 炒<br />\n搶購出手 個罩貴到飛起<br />\n<br />\n來全城 炒 炒 炒 炒 炒<br />\n大量買入再炒 疫症會 核爆準備<br />\n<br />\n二百蚊 有一包 五十個<br />\n原價比起要貴得多<br />\n一聽起 我就有火<br />\n盡快盡快埋去排 來多喼想再拖<br />\n<br />\n插隊的 必須再排過<br />\n逐個撼低對方一個二個 我但求全清貨<br />\nOh Let's Buy！<br />\n <code>#Repeat</code><br />\n<br />\n<code>Guitar Solo ♪♪♪</code><br />\n<br />\n六百蚊 得一包 四十個<br />\n原價比起再貴得多<br />\n一聽起 我就有火<br />\n外國存貨亦冇埋 淘寶的都照拖<br />\n<br />\n最慘的 聽朝再嚟過<br />\n逐個派籌派得一兩十個 我踢閘唔收貨<br />\nOh Let's Fight！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿叔踢閘重溫:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3177178759056825/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F3177178759056825%2F&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9BURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=5015b41c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3177178759056825/</a>"},{"pid":"6605907a07a3ebb5d9371478fc4f0dd63b245a47","tid":1857303,"uid":103783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:29:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2zx-wdO0L20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2zx-wdO0L20&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9BURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=c89076e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2zx-wdO0L20</a>"},{"pid":"3cb5f63e3001bd858a646a50602ee786bde41733","tid":18